headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid CSX and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the last six months, CSX’s shares have sunk to $30.02, producing a disappointing 11.9% loss while the S&P 500 was flat. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
